snippet.title: Best VGM 1779 - Divinity 2 : Ego Draconis - Broken Valley Wakes
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1180 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dj8Qe3GUrdc

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Xbox 360 / PC
Divinity II : Ego Draconis (2010)
Broken Valley Wakes
Kirill Pokrovsky
